{"tid":2342262,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"鐘意咗一個唔應該鐘意嘅人，點忘記佢？","createTime":"2020-12-27T03:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T17:11:01.000Z","uid":67203,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9f28b962231fada2e57bf209265eb18b28201416","tid":2342262,"uid":67203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T03:58:46.000Z","msg":"以前從來未試過鐘意非單身嘅人。講起上黎好奇怪，但我真係咁：每逢識到一個異性，當知道佢有另一半/已婚，潛意識會令我對呢個人冇興趣，唔會鐘意佢<br />\n<br />\n但係終於瀨野了。我鐘意咗一個有另一半嘅同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（公司有個女同事最鐘意問人地感情狀況<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，問完仲會周圍講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當鐘意咗一個唔應該鐘意嘅人，大概有三種做法：<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">1. 照衝</span><br />\n我有道德觀念嘅，就算對方未結婚，我都唔想做人第三者破壞人地。不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"orange\">2. 繼續暗戀，將呢份心情埋喺心底</span><br />\n我唔想繼續鐘意佢。一黎我好難專心工作/鐘意過第二個人；二黎我驚自己會越黎越鐘意佢，無法自拔，有日我會忍唔住想搶人<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">3. 放棄，儘快忘記佢</span><br />\n呢個選擇係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但點先可以忘記一個人？嗰個人係我同事，工作上有接觸，日對夜對&hellip;好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又驚俾人知我暗戀佢，又要每日壓抑自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好難轉工，因為依家份工好啱我<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6b7a4ffa68d7f92c82e63d80d1a0e6e449dc37","tid":2342262,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T04:04:40.000Z","msg":"gay? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d608dec106d52a34292143bc3262d8dc964c7e4","tid":2342262,"uid":239100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T04:06:20.000Z","msg":"No.3"},{"pid":"da5fd3b4a5964c00049